 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the upward momentum\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the release\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The celebration in Toulouse, Airbus' global headquarters, where the plane was built and painted, was attended by the airline's top 100 employees known as 'Chairman's Club Honorees' nominated from divisions across the company.\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1203, \"end\": 1211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toulouse\", \"score\": 0.9999978702962776, \"rank\": 1.8101040035374626e-06, \"text\": \"Toulouse\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toulouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toulouse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The celebration\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"Airbus' global headquarters\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"the plane\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"the airline's top 100 employees\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1328}, {\"ngram\": \"Chairman's Club Honorees\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"divisions\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2023 'honorees' unveiled the brand-new Team USA 'livery' design and were the first to fly on the newly minted plane, as recognition of their commitment and dedication to the brand.\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999995471492755, \"rank\": 4.422673721402316e-07, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2023 'honorees\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1429}, {\"ngram\": \"the newly minted plane\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"recognition\", \"from\": 1